%U A395064 18888888888999999999999999,33399999999999999999999999999,88888888888888888888888888888888,66888888888888888888888999999999999
%N A395064 a(n) is the smallest positive integer such that s^n = p where s is the sum of digits of a(n) (cf. A007953) and p is the product of digits of a(n) (cf. A007954).
%e A395064 a(3) = 666666 as the digital sum of 666666 is 36 and the product of digits of 666666 is 36^3 and 666666 is the smallest number with this property.
%Y A395064 Cf. A002473, A007953, A007954, A009994, A117720, A274124, A379834.
